title: Ozzy Osbourne - Tribute 2 (KBFH Pre.FM) 1981 ak320
description:
Ozzy Osbourne - Tribute 2 (KBFH Pre.FM) 1981 ak320

Ozzy/Randy Rhoads 5-11-81 Cleveland, OH (Unedited Tribute Show)
This is the unedited version of what would become the randy rhoads tribute cd.... a great show by Ozzy and Randy and excellent quality

Tracklist


1 -Intro
2- I Don't Know
3- Crazy Train
4- Believer
5- Mr Crowley
6- Flying High Again
7- Revelation (Mother Earth)
8- Steal Away (The Night)
9- Tommy Aldridge Drum Solo
10- Suicide Solution
11- Randy Rhoads Guitar solo
12- Iron Man
13- Children Of The Grave
14- Paranoid

Players
Ozzy Osbourne - vocals
Randy Rhoads - guitar
Rudy Sarzo - bass
Tommy Aldridge - drums
Don Airey - keyboards
